{"tid":2420401,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（恥笑）班索斯林連僅有嘅獨佔優勢無無埋，平台玩家最後何去何從","createTime":"2021-02-24T02:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T04:55:14.000Z","uid":108519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c557c7e0e9c50280e7ee9b93d734933e825f9e","tid":2420401,"uid":108519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>索尼互動娛樂總裁兼首席執行官Jim Ryan在接受CQ採訪時表示隨著春季的到來，越來越多的PS遊戲將登陸PC，已經確認的是PS4獨占遊戲《Days Gone》即將於春季發售PC版。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJim Ryan表示：<br />\n<br />\n在2021年初，我們的工作室和他們開發的遊戲比以往任何時候都要好。特別是在PS4生命週期的後期，我們製作了一些精彩和偉大的遊戲並展示給玩家。<br />\n<br />\n此外，讓PC端玩家玩到這些獨占遊戲也更加便利，因此我們決定將更多PS遊戲帶到PC平台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/23/22297091/days-gone-pc-playstation-games-ports-jim-ryan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2021%2F2%2F23%2F22297091%2Fdays-gone-pc-playstation-games-ports-jim-ryan&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=45174dd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/23/22297091/days-gone-pc-playstation-games-ports-jim-ryan</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑L死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdfb1127fed24f65a28c1112c1369a1b7d6587d","tid":2420401,"uid":317956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:29:36.000Z","msg":"佢地可以講平好多同無外掛"},{"pid":"fa4a07a1691a509964a8593d9466968bbc6a05fc","tid":2420401,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcdfb1127fed24f65a28c1112c1369a1b7d6587d","tid":2420401,"uid":317956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:29:36.000Z","msg":"佢地可以講平好多同無外掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />steam成日都特價，單機game唔驚外掛"},{"pid":"9190aa9f4a9d5d7da183a1a442ae54218c030659","tid":2420401,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:35:48.000Z","